      <data key="d1">"Formula 1 is a high-speed motorsport event characterized by intense competition among teams and drivers, known for its meticulous preparation and celebration of victories."&lt;SEP&gt;"Formula 1 is a high-stakes motor racing event known for its intense competition and strategic maneuvers among drivers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Formula 1 is a premier international racing organization that hosts highly competitive racing events on various tracks worldwide."&lt;SEP&gt;"Formula 1 is a prestigious motorsport event and organization, indicating high standards and competitive nature within the sport."&lt;SEP&gt;"Formula 1 is a prestigious motorsport organization known for hosting high-profile racing events, including the Canadian Grand Prix mentioned in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Formula 1 is an international motorsport organization that governs the racing events and awards associated with the FIA Awards."</data>
