      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Celebration encapsulates the essence of the award ceremony as a gathering to recognize and honor accomplishments within the rally racing community."&lt;SEP&gt;"Celebration encompasses the joy and excitement experienced by racers and teams during and after the go-kart racing event."&lt;SEP&gt;"Celebration encompasses the joyful moments experienced by teams and drivers after a successful race, reflecting their achievements and camaraderie."&lt;SEP&gt;"Celebration refers to the events and festivities held following a race victory, highlighting achievements in the Formula One series."&lt;SEP&gt;"Celebration refers to the overarching atmosphere of joy and recognition present at the awards ceremony for accomplishments in motorsports."</data>
