    <node id="&quot;THE PODIUM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Podium is a designated area at the FIA Awards where presenters and award recipients engage with the audience and announce achievements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a designated area during the event where award recipients stand to receive accolades and where speakers deliver important messages."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a featured physical structure in the ceremony where presenters and award recipients stand, adorned with the FIA Awards 2023 logo and geometric designs."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a key feature of the awards ceremony, used for presenting awards and speeches, enhancing the formal atmosphere of the event."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a physical structure at the awards ceremony where winners stand to receive trophies, symbolizing achievement in the FIA World Endurance Championship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a significant feature of the award ceremony where winners are recognized and awarded for their achievements in motorsport."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is a stage area where presenters and award recipients interact during the FIA Formula E Awards, serving as a focal point of the event."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is the physical location where the FIA Awards ceremony takes place, featuring presenters and award distributions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is the physical structure where awards are presented during ceremonies, including the FIA Awards."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is the stage area where the awards are presented during the FIA Awards, serving as a central focal point for celebration and recognition of rally racing achievements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is the stage at the FIA Awards where award presentations and speeches take place, central to the event's proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium is the stage where awards are presented during the FIA AWARDS KIGALI 2024, serving as a focal point for the event."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium represents the elevated stage setup at the FIA Awards 2023 where winners are recognized and celebrated."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Podium represents the stage where award recipients stand to accept their trophies, symbolizing recognition and achievement in motorsport."</data>
